snippet.title: To Clean The Mountain Trailer
snippet.description:
To Clean The Mountain is a platforming adventure where you throw yourself towards the summit. The spirit of the mountain will talk with you as you traverse a variety of environments. 

Main Channel for the Game:
https://www.youtube.com/@YinzStudio

Try out the demo and wish list the game here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3138520/To_Clean_The_Mountain/?beta=0
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3138600/To_Clean_The_Mountain_Demo/
